<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Package Status Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: #e72828;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: white;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .tracking-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: #e72828;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: #34495e;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .tracking-number {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #e72828;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 3px solid #e72828;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Sussex Logistics</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{receiverName}},</p>

            <p>There has been an update to your package status:</p>

            <div class="tracking-info">
                <p>Tracking Number: <span class="tracking-number">{{trackingId}}</span></p>
                <div class="details">
                    <p><strong>Status Update:</strong> {{statusUpdate}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Current Location:</strong> {{currentLocation}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Expected Delivery:</strong> {{expectedDeliveryDate}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>


            <p>Track your package's complete journey by clicking below:</p>

            <center>
                <a href="https://sussex-logistics.vercel.app/package/{{trackingId}}" class="button">
                    Track Your Package
                </a>
            </center>

            <p>Package Details:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Shipping Method: {{typeOfShipment}}</li>
                <li>Carrier: {{carrier}}</li>
                <li>Delivery Address: {{receiverAddress}}</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Need assistance? Our customer service team is here to help.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to {{receiverEmailAddress}}</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} SUSSEX Logistics. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://sussex-logistics.vercel.app">Visit Our Website</a> |
                <a href="https://sussex-logistics.vercel.app/contact">Contact Us</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>